Description:
A set of macros to make calls to alloc/calloc/realloc safer.

Files:
lib/safe-alloc.h
lib/safe-alloc.c
m4/safe-alloc.m4

Depends-on:
calloc-gnu
reallocarray

configure.ac:
gl_SAFE_ALLOC

Makefile.am:
lib_SOURCES += safe-alloc.c

Include:
"safe-alloc.h"

